title: Dem's Recession Tax Hikes
description: Fellas discuss the latest Dem plan to raise taxes, this time in a recession. Christina Nolan joins the progrum for a conversation about her race for Senate from Vermont. And Kendall Qualls of TakeCharge shares details on his new documentary, "I Am A Victor."
author: hello@ruthlesspodcast.com (Kendall Qualls, Christina Nolan, Josh Holmes, Michael Duncan, John Ashbrook, Comfortably Smug)
